summary: This is an email chain from October 22, 2019, regarding the cancellation of a conference call line that was to be used for speaking with an Epstein victim and her attorneys. The call was originally scheduled for that afternoon around 4pm.

events.title: Cancelled Conference Call with Epstein Victim
events.description: A conference call line scheduled for around 4pm to speak with an Epstein victim and her attorneys was cancelled.

keyFacts: A conference call involving an Epstein victim and her attorneys was scheduled for the afternoon of October 22, 2019.
The conference call was cancelled on the same day it was to occur.
The victim's attorneys were noted to be in different physical locations.
The document is an internal email chain regarding logistical arrangements for legal communication.
